<section xml:id="mysqlnd-uh.configuration" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook">
 &reftitle.runtime;
 &extension.runtime;
 <para>
  <table>
   <title>&ConfigureOptions; Mysqlnd_uh</title>
   <tgroup cols="4">
    <thead>
     <row>
      <entry>&Name;</entry>
      <entry>&Default;</entry>
      <entry>&Changeable;</entry>
      <entry>&Changelog;</entry>
     </row>
    </thead>
    <tbody xml:id="mysqlnd-uh.configuration.list">
     <row>
      <entry><link linkend="ini.mysqlnd-uh.enable">mysqlnd_uh.enable</link></entry>
      <entry>1</entry>
      <entry>PHP_INI_SYSTEM</entry>
      <entry><!-- leave empty, this will be filled by an automatic script --></entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry><link linkend="ini.mysqlnd-uh.report-wrong-types">mysqlnd_uh.report_wrong_types</link></entry>
      <entry>1</entry>
      <entry>PHP_INI_ALL</entry>
      <entry><!-- leave empty, this will be filled by an automatic script --></entry>
     </row>
    </tbody>
   </tgroup>
  </table>
 </para>

 &ini.descriptions.title;

 <para>
  <variablelist>
   <varlistentry xml:id="ini.mysqlnd-uh.enable">
     <term>
      <parameter>mysqlnd_uh.enable</parameter>
      <type>int</type>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       Active ou désactive le plugin. Si désactivé, l'extension
       ne va pas autoriser les utilisateurs à le connexer à
       <link linkend="book.mysqlnd">mysqlnd</link> pour interception
       les appels à <link linkend="book.mysqlnd">mysqlnd</link>.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>
    <varlistentry xml:id="ini.mysqlnd-uh.report-wrong-types">
     <term>
      <parameter>mysqlnd_uh.report_wrong_types</parameter>
      <type>int</type>
     </term>
     <listitem>
      <para>
       Si l'on doit rapporter des types de valeurs retournées erronées
       comme des erreurs de niveau <constant>E_WARNING</constant>.
       Il est vivement recommandé d'utiliser cette configuration
       pour détecter les erreurs.
      </para>
     </listitem>
    </varlistentry>

  </variablelist>
 </para>
</section>

